rComments: Marga is such a G she was so passionate and clearly cared for all of her students. Taught the course with her husband Mark Solovey and they were both good at explaining everything. They give you the questions for the midterm and final like 2 weeks in advance because they don't want to stress you out.
Took this class taught by her and Mark Solovey, best choice that I've made in Uni so far. They post slides online so you don't really need to attend lectures. Nicest prof I've had so far

This course, also taught w Prof Solovey was the best decision I made in taking a first year course. Very intriguing and they are such passionate and caring profs. Tutorials for this course are a little unnecessary as the course is very straightforward. Great course to take in first year to introduce yourself to university. but, not a bird course.
learned and was not stressed for once, mandatory tutorials but they summarized course content and helped when the tests came around, tests were very fair and course was intresting
She's really funny and intelligent. Brought so much to the course. I really liked her!
barely did any work for this class and still did really well. you probably wont even have to study that much as long as you attend the lecs.
